      "severity": "CRITICAL",
      "scar_class": "TOOLCHAIN_DESIGN (v1 partial execute → rollback → v2 healed)",
      "function_broken": "v1 script `echo $ref_files | while read` FAIL với filename có space + Unicode NFD (macOS HFS/APFS decompose 'đổi' = \\304\\221\\341\\273\\225i). git grep -l wrap filename \"...\" + bash $() strip NUL bytes → sed nhận literal quote chars → 'No such file'. Partial execute: 16 rename + 4 ref patch + crash ở 5th patch.",
      "evidence": "Container test bash 5: `x=$(printf 'a\\0b\\0c\\0'); ${#x}=15 (strip NUL)` + warning 'command substitution: ignored null byte in input'. Process substitution `< <(...)` preserve NUL đúng — 3 records.",
      "remedy": "Rollback hard reset → ship v2 với `git grep -z + read -d '' + < <(process substitution)`. Commit 2A.1 fix 49456e5. Re-execute → 50 patches clean.",
      "heal_status": "healed_with_v2",
      "bai_hoc": "git grep -l output wrap filename có space/special trong \"...\". $() strip NUL. Mọi script xử lý filename từ git grep PHẢI dùng `-z` + `read -d ''` + process substitution. KHÔNG pipe `echo | while`. Vaccin này upgrade scope SCAR-20260424-RUNTIME-MISMATCH-BASH3.2: không chỉ bash version compat, còn filesystem encoding (NFD/NFC) + filename special chars."
    },
